OL,3,CDrivers face fines for reversing on
OL,4,Chard shoulder after serious crash
OL,6,FMore than a dozen drivers have been
OL,7,Fissued fines for reversing on the hard
OL,8,Fshoulder on the A2 whilst police dealt
OL,9,Fwith a crash.
OL,11,FOfficers and emergency services were
OL,12,Fcalled to the A2 Watling Street
OL,13,Fcoastbound, near Gravesend, on Sunday
OL,14,F(23 November) following a collision
OL,15,Fbetween two cars and a lorry.
OL,17,FKent Police say there were
OL,18,F"unavoidable delays" whilst crews
OL,19,Fworked at the scene to help those
OL,20,Finvolved.
