OL,3,CDrivers face fines for reversing on
OL,4,Chard shoulder after serious crash
OL,6,FThe force says some drivers got
OL,7,Fimpatient and decided to reverse along
OL,8,Fthe hard shoulder to return to an
OL,9,Fearlier slip road, with a small number
OL,10,Fturning around to do so.
OL,12,FA total of 16 drivers were reported
OL,13,Fand are now at risk of receiving a
OL,14,F#100 fine and three points on their
OL,15,Flicence.
