OL,3,CDrivers face fines for reversing on
OL,4,Chard shoulder after serious crash
OL,6,FInspector David Crompton said:
OL,7,F"Officers fully appreciate the
OL,8,Ffrustration of being stuck in traffic.
OL,9,FHowever, we close roads for only as
OL,10,Flong as is necessary, whether that's
OL,11,Fto assist casualties, investigate life
OL,12,Fthreatening collisions, or clear the
OL,13,Froad of debris that could damage cars
OL,14,For lead to further accidents.
OL,16,F"Those using the hard shoulder for
OL,17,Fanything other than a lawful reason
OL,18,Fcould obstruct emergency vehicles
OL,19,Fheading towards a serious collision,
OL,20,Fimpacting injured drivers.
